From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 01:48:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] feat: premium component-level visual upgrades

Enhance glass-card with gradient border + deeper hover glow.
Buttons gain gradient shift + scale(1.02) hover, scale(0.98) active.
Stat grid gets vertical gradient dividers.
Phase numbers get accent ring with radial yellow glow.
Nav adds animated yellow underline (spring layoutId) + mobile slide-in from right with backdrop blur.
New CSS utilities: dot-grid-bg, drift-dots, progress-bar-fill, filter-pill, cursor-glow, mobile-ring-decor.
